---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Now" description="What I am focusing on now.">
  <article class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl">
      <header class="mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-6xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">NOW</h1>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-100">
          This is my <a href="https://nownownow.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-foreground transition-colors">now</a> page,
          giving an overview of the things I am doing currently. For finding out more about me,
          you can read <a href="/about" class="underline underline-offset-4 hover:text-foreground transition-colors">about</a>.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose">
        <blockquote>
          Last update was on 06.05.2025
        </blockquote>

        <h3>Studying AI Agents (i.e. smolagents, ag2, crewai)</h3>

        <h3>Taking 2x a week spanish language classes on Preply.com</h3>

        <h3>Embracing the role of being a parent</h3>

        <h3>Working on smart.AI</h3>

        <h3>Listening to silence</h3>

        <h3>Reading</h3>
        <p>
          <a href="https://www.amazon.de/-/en/Coming-Wave-Technology-Twenty-first-Centurys/dp/0593593952" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            "The Coming Wave"
          </a> by Mustafa Suleyman and
          <a href="https://www.amazon.de/-/en/Creativity-Inc-Overcoming-Unseen-Inspiration/dp/0812993012" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Creativity.Inc
          </a> by Ed Catmull
        </p>

        <h3>Working Out 3x a week</h3>

        <details class="mt-12">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground transition-colors">
            Historical Versions
          </summary>
          <p class="mt-4 text-muted-foreground">No History Yet</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
